attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Remarkable corner penthouse in coveted City Point! Discover luxury living in this exceptional 2 bed PLUS versatile office, 2.5-bath PH with THREE heated garage parking spaces in a boutique elevator building. The open-concept living and kitchen area is designed for both comfort and entertaining, featuring a gas fireplace, Wolf/Sub Zero appliances, double oven, wine fridge, and a massive center island with additional dining space. A versatile office / den leads to a full staircase and a head house equipped with a wet bar. The private roof deck with beautiful city views + direct gas line for a fire pit + grilling, plus an outdoor TV. On the bedroom level, the primary suite is a retreat in itself, boasting a large walk-in closet, a marble bath with a steam shower, a separate freestanding tub, and a double sink vanity. The second bed and bath are both generous in size! Additional highlights include an elevator, deeded storage locker, visual intercom system, + 3 zones of built-in audio.
